CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Healthy Choice Wellness Corp. is a holding company focused on providing consumers with healthier daily choices with respect to nutrition and other lifestyle alternatives. It consists of the subsidiaries that operate the HCMC retail natural grocery stores, namely Adas Natural Market, Paradise Health and Nutrition, Mother Earths Storehouse, Greens Natural Foods and Ellwood Thompsons as well as the Healthy Choice Wellness Centers and the online entity thevitaminstore.com.
